data.description: Three family apartment in great shape no need to do anything but move in or collect your rents.  Low maintenance siding, newer windows and roof is 3 years old. Garage is huge and can be converted back to 3 bays.  Hardwood floors in most rooms. Let the rents pay for some of your mortgage. First floor could be a 3 bedroom, 2nd floor 2 beds and 3rd has one bedroom.  Separate utilities as well. Coin-op washer and dryer in basement.  Take a look at this nice 3 family you wont be sorry.  All offers will be presented on Monday May, 9.
